      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Experience automotive excellence with this impeccably preserved specimen, presented in true showroom condition. Meticulously maintained and showing virtually no signs of wear, this vehicle represents the pinnacle of its class. From the flawless exterior finish to the pristine, smoke-free interior, every detail reflects a history of uncompromising care. Complete with a comprehensive service record and all original documentation, this is a rare opportunity for the discerning enthusiast who demands nothing less than perfection.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
