    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Step into a lost era of elegance with this automotive masterpiece. Every curve of its hand-polished silhouette whispers stories of moonlit coastal drives and the raw, unbridled spirit of the open road. This isn't just a car; it's a time capsule, preserved with a reverence that borders on the sacred. From the tactile click of the chrome switches to the deep, resonant hum of the engine\u2014a mechanical symphony that stirs the soul\u2014this vehicle offers an analog purity that modern machines simply cannot replicate. It sits poised and breathtaking, waiting for a driver who understands that some legends don't just age; they transcend.",
      "price": 48900.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 41
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional example of automotive excellence. This vehicle arrives in pristine, showroom condition, having been meticulously maintained to the highest standards. With its flawless exterior finish and an interior that retains its original luster, this is a rare opportunity for the discerning buyer who demands nothing less than perfection. Every detail reflects a commitment to quality, ensuring a driving experience that feels indistinguishable from new.",
