    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there, fellow car lovers! It truly breaks my heart to let this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for a new chapter. I\u2019ve babied this car since day one\u2014always garaged, hand-washed every Sunday, and it still looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor. It\u2019s in absolutely pristine shape, practically flawless inside and out. You won\u2019t find another one cared for quite like this; it\u2019s a real gem that\u2019s been the pride of my driveway. Come by for a coffee and a look, I\u2019m sure you\u2019ll fall in love with it just like I did!",
